类 Schedule

java.lang.Object
com.study.journey.entity.Schedule
public class Schedule extends Object
The Schedule class represents a weekly schedule. It contains properties representing each day of the week, from Monday to Sunday. The class provides getters and setters for these properties. copyright : Copyright (c) 2023/5/26
